<div class="p-6 bg-white shadow rounded-md mb-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Write and Publish Articles</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    This page is your content creation center. Here, you can craft articles from scratch,
    format them for readability, add media, and publish them for your audience. It’s designed
    to make publishing fast, intuitive, and professional.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-4 mb-2">Sections Included:</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
    <li><strong>Title & Subtitle:</strong> Define your article headline and subheading to attract readers.</li>
    <li><strong>Content Editor:</strong> A rich text editor to write, format, and style your content.</li>
    <li><strong>Media Upload:</strong> Upload images, videos, or infographics to make your article engaging.</li>
    <li><strong>Category Selection:</strong> Assign a category and tags so readers can easily find your content.</li>
