    <li><strong>Publish & Schedule:</strong> Either publish immediately or schedule for a later date/time.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-4 mb-2">Purpose of This Page:</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
    The Write Article page empowers creators to share their knowledge, stories, or insights
    with the world. By structuring content properly, adding multimedia, and categorizing it
    effectively, your articles reach the right audience and increase engagement.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-4 mb-2">Why Each Section Matters:</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
    <li>Title & Subtitle help grab reader attention instantly.</li>
    <li>Content Editor allows for creative and professional writing.</li>
    <li>Media Upload improves visual appeal and reader retention.</li>
    <li>Category Selection ensures discoverability and SEO benefits.</li>
